      <title>财政部将拍卖 1250 亿美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/treasury-to-sell-125-billion-in-debt-at-auction-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部将在下周的季度再融资拍卖中出售 1250 亿美元债券。长期债券销售指导保持不变。美国贸易逆差也飙升至 980 亿美元。彭博社的 Michael McKee 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/treasury-to-sell-125-billion-in-debt-at-auction-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 14:18:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长莱恩表示，通胀风险下需要灵活调整利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/ecb-lane-says-agility-needed-on-rates-amid-inflation-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行首席经济学家菲利普·莱恩表示，由于通胀风险仍然存在，欧洲央行应保持灵活的货币政策制定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/ecb-lane-says-agility-needed-on-rates-amid-inflation-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 14:17:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦格理关闭美国债务资本市场，以应对私人信贷转型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/macquarie-shuts-us-debt-capital-markets-in-private-credit-pivot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，麦格理集团有限公司 (Macquarie Group Ltd.) 正在关闭其美国债务资本市场部门，该部门的业务包括杠杆贷款发放、银团贷款和交易，以将资源集中在私人信贷上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/macquarie-shuts-us-debt-capital-markets-in-private-credit-pivot</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 14:10:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雪佛龙就委内瑞拉问题与特朗普政府进行接触</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/chevron-is-in-contact-with-trump-administration-over-venezuela</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些共和党人呼吁美国撤销雪佛龙公司在委内瑞拉的经营许可，但雪佛龙公司正在与特朗普政府保持沟通。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/chevron-is-in-contact-with-trump-administration-over-venezuela</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 14:04:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雪佛龙首席执行官称特朗普上任后能源观念发生改变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/view-on-energy-has-changed-under-trump-says-chevron-ceo-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雪佛龙董事长兼首席执行官迈克·沃思讨论了唐纳德·特朗普总统领导下的能源前景。他说，该公司正在以更“资本高效的方式”向市场提供更多能源。他在“彭博监测”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/view-on-energy-has-changed-under-trump-says-chevron-ceo-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 14:02:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国企业 1 月新增就业岗位 183,000 个：ADP</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/us-companies-add-183-000-jobs-in-january-adp-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据 ADP 研究所周三发布的数据，美国 1 月份企业就业人数增幅超过预期，私营企业就业人数上月增加 183,000 人。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视台上对这些数字进行了详细分析。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/us-companies-add-183-000-jobs-in-january-adp-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:53:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任期临近、关税承诺出台，美国贸易逆差大幅膨胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/us-trade-gap-ballooned-ahead-of-trump-term-tariff-promises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普第二任期开始前进口激增以及他兑现全面关税承诺，美国贸易逆差在 2024 年底急剧扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/us-trade-gap-ballooned-ahead-of-trump-term-tariff-promises</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:31:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大与美国的贸易顺差因石油而创 2022 年以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/canada-s-trade-surplus-with-us-widens-on-crude-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年年底，加拿大对美国的能源出口大幅增加，推动加拿大与其最大客户的贸易顺差达到两年多来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/canada-s-trade-surplus-with-us-widens-on-crude-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国邮政局撤销暂停向中国发货的决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/us-postal-service-says-it-s-accepting-china-hong-kong-packages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国邮政局表示，将接受来自中国和香港邮政的“所有国际入境邮件和包裹”，撤回了几个小时前宣布的暂停部分海外货运的公告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/us-postal-service-says-it-s-accepting-china-hong-kong-packages</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:10:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易战担忧盖过特朗普对伊朗施压 油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美国和中国之间的贸易战将损害全球经济增长，以及美国总统唐纳德·特朗普加大对欧佩克成员国伊朗的经济压力，油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 23:33:21 GMT</pubDate>
